{"error":0,"message":"","data":[{"show_ID":"1992","airdate":"1513515600","name_switch":"off","DJ":"IImmortal vs PhasedBased","showname":"Sunday Detox","blurb":"Hi all,\nIt has been a few years and it took some work and determination to get back again. But with some serious help from PhasedBased we are finally back. I would like to invite you to join us for a lazy Sunday afternoon, feeling the hangover just slip away while we listen to some easy going tunes.","nice_showname":"<strong><big>IImmortal vs PhasedBased<\/big><\/strong><br \/>Sunday Detox","nice_airdate":"Sunday 17th December, 2017<br \/>at 14:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"2008","airdate":"1513710000","name_switch":"off","DJ":"ziona and maybe Slaygon","showname":"Pre-Christmas with master LMan","blurb":"Hello Everyone! \n\nWe finish this year slightly before christmas, and we have an amazing guest coming up! LMan, a real SID wizard and remixer joins us for an interview, you can also ask anything you wanted to know about him. And since this looks like the last show of the year from ziona (and maybe Slaygon), we wish you a Merry Christmas and a Very Happy New Year too! Gonna be back on 2nd January.\n","nice_showname":"<strong><big>ziona and maybe Slaygon<\/big><\/strong><br \/>Pre-Christmas with master LMan","nice_airdate":"Tuesday 19th December, 2017<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"2009","airdate":"1513882800","name_switch":"off","DJ":"KraxxUltima","showname":"The Ultimate Winter Solstice","blurb":"We're getting close to Xmas ,and in case Santa might be wearing a eyepatch, shugging rum and yelling Arrrrr! while balancing on a pegleg,..We still have a show going down. Request your favorite C64 or Amiga tunes and enjoy winter solstice! ","nice_showname":"<strong><big>KraxxUltima<\/big><\/strong><br \/>The Ultimate Winter Solstice","nice_airdate":"Thursday 21st December, 2017<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"}]}